### get_commits
Get commit history for a repository or file.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| owner | string | Yes | - | Repository owner |
| repo | string | Yes | - | Repository name |
| ref | string\|null | No | null | Branch, tag, or SHA |
| path | string\|null | No | null | Filter by file path |
| limit | integer | No | 20 | Maximum commits |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "githubmcp", toolName: "get_commits", arguments: { owner: "octocat", repo: "Hello-World", limit: 10 } })

